<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title style="color: red;">Welcome to History of Vintage Royal Enfield Bike</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #fbe9e7; /* skin color */
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #8e4585; /* violet color */
            color: white;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 200px;
            height: auto;
        }
        .bike-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .bike-info {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            width: 300px;
        }
        .bike-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .bike-title {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .bike-details {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <img src="logo.png" alt="Vintage Royal Enfield Logo" class="logo">
    </header>

    <div class="bike-container">
        <!-- Bike 1 -->
        <div class="bike-info">
            <img src="royal-enfield-model-7b2b.jpg" alt="Vintage Royal Enfield Model 1" class="bike-image">
            <h2 class="bike-title">Royal Enfield Model 7B2B</h2>
            <p class="bike-details">This is a vintage Royal Enfield motorcycle model 7B2B. It was manufactured in the 1950s and is known for its classic design and robust engine.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Bike 2 -->
        <div class="bike-info">
            <img src="royal-enfield-model-k-976-cc-9020-cd98.jpg" alt="Vintage Royal Enfield Model K" class="bike-image">
            <h2 class="bike-title">Royal Enfield Model K 976cc</h2>
            <p class="bike-details">This is a vintage Royal Enfield Model K with a 976cc engine. It was manufactured in the 1930s and is considered a rare and valuable collector's item.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Add more bike info blocks here -->
    </div>
</body>
</html>
